
Changelog
=========

0.2 (in developement)
---------------------

 - https encryption support
 - option to listen only on localhost
 - config and databases reside now in the user's home directory
 - savable playlists
 - added GPL license
 - salted user passwords
 - admin user can be created inside web-interface on first start
 - playlists are periodically saved in the session, so they're
   not lost, when the browser or tabs are closed etc.
 - theming support
 - configurable server port 
 - admin panel for creating new users
 - welcome screen for CLI and web-interface

0.1 (2012-08-16)
----------------

Initial Release
